parameters:
"It's been a while since I've been here, but it doesn't seem
much has changed! Which game should I play... Hm?"

"Just like I was told... I've been here since morning...
spending time... What should I do next... Ah...♡"

"(Could that be Makoto!? No mistake about it! I can't
believe I'd run into her here!)"

"Ma, Mamoru...? Why are you here... Of all times... this
timing..."

"Wha!? There's no way I can do that! ...Nn♡... Ugh, okay...
I'll obey."

"Hey, Mamoru. What a coincidence...♡ What brings you to a
place like this... Ah♡"

"I just happened to stop by. More importantly, aren't you
supposed to be helping out at the dojo today?"

"Eh?... Uh... Well... It seems our master fell ill
again...♡"

"So, the dojo was suddenly closed! I came here on a whim
since I had already made the trip for nothing!"

"He's of an old age... Ah♡... He really shouldn't be
overexerting himself! Our master can be such a handful!
Ahahahaha!"

"I just happened to stop by. More importantly, aren't you
supposed to be helping out at the dojo today?"

"Didn't you tell your followers? That you'd be giving
martial arts lessons. You better head to the dojo or you'll
be late, won't you?"
"Eh?... Ah, ah! ...♡ What! You knew about the dojo!"

"Well, that makes things easier! Actually, the dojo was
suddenly closed today! So, I ended up here since I had
already made the trip for nothing!"

"Apparently, the master threw out his back! He's of an old
age... Ah♡... He really shouldn't be overexerting himself!"

"...Makoto? Are you feeling okay? And were you talking to
someone just now?"

"No, that's not possible! I've been alone the whole time!
And I'm perfectly fine! If you want, I can even dance for
you right now!"

"Eh, eh? You don't have to do that... Oh! Since we're
here... Do you want to hang out together today?"

"That sounds great!! ...♡♡♡ I was just thinking... of
inviting you... Nn♡..."

"Really? Then let's start from the back and work our way
forward! I'm so happy to be able to play with Makoto. What
should we start with?"

Talking to Makoto after such a long time, something seemed
off. Her face looked a bit red, and her spirits were
unusually high. But I was so happy to be playing together, I
didn't press the matter further.

parameters:
"Man, that was fun! Arcades really are the best! How many
years has it been since we played a racing game together?"

"The new dance game they added was fun too! Just moving
along with the screen made it feel like we were really
dancing!"

"And then, the game where you shoot up the screen with guns!
That was a blast! Hey, why don't we go play it one more
time?"

"...Makoto, are you okay? You've been out of it, are you
sure you're not feeling unwell...?"

"Heh!? No, that's not it at all! Man~! Every game was really
fun!"

"It's been a while since I've had this much fun! Playing in
the arcade once in a while isn't bad at all!"

"Really? If you say so... But, Makoto. It's weird to say
this here, but actually, on that day..."
"Sorry, I've got a call! Just wait a moment, okay?"

"Hey, you're late... Hurry up and stop this... Eh? No,
but... I'm playing with Mamoru right now..."

parameters:
"Sorry Mamoru, something urgent came up... Can we continue
this conversation... another day...?"

"Uh, sure. It's fine... But are you sure nothing's
wrong...?"

"I'm really sorry! I have to go right now! I'll definitely
make it up to you! See you tomorrow then!"

"Ah, Makoto! ...She's gone. I couldn't apologize to Makoto
again."

(Even so, Makoto was strangely sexy today. She's usually so
gallant, but today she seemed... erotic.)

(No, no, what am I thinking? This is disrespectful to
Makoto... I shouldn't be entertaining such foolish thoughts.
I better head home quickly too.)

The next morning, I was in a particularly good mood as I got
ready. I had fun hanging out yesterday, and I thought I'd be
able to go to school with Makoto again. But there was no
sign of her outside my house, so I ended up going to school
alone again.
